### Variáveis
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api
@token = Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. Dashboard Administrativo
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard/admin
Authorization: {{token}}

### 2. Dashboard do Hospital (ID 1)
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard/hospital/1
Authorization: {{token}}

### 3. Dashboard do Hospital (ID 2)
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard/hospital/2
Authorization: {{token}}

### 4. Dashboard de Hospital Inexistente (deve retornar 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard/hospital/999
Authorization: {{token}}
